</head>
<body style = "height : 100%">
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center bg-secondary text-light ps-3" style = "height : 10vh ;">
    <div id ="menubutton" class = "btn">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="2em" height="2em" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-list" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.5 12a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h10a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H3a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5zm0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h10a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H3a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5zm0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h10a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H3a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5z"/>
          </svg></div>
        <h1 class="ms-4"><%= subject.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + subject.slice(1) %> Practice Test</h1></div>
    <div class = "container-float overflow-hidden p-2" style = "height : 80vh" id="contentcontainer">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-9 border-end border-4 border-dark d-flex flex-column" style = "height : 80vh ;">
                <div class="border-bottom border-3 border-dark">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                        <h2><%= subject.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + subject.slice(1) %></h2>
                        <h2 class = "font-monospace"><span id="hours">01</span>:<span id="minutes">00</span>:<span id="seconds">00</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
    <div class = "d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
    <h2 id="questionnumber">Question : 1</h2>
    <button id="resetbutton">Reset</button>
    </div>
    <div class="overflow-auto fs-5">
    <p class = "statement" id = "0" >
        Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Autem doloribus assumenda voluptas qui saepe provident tempora, nisi, cumque nam explicabo maiores temporibus ducimus quam aspernatur omnis quibusdam sunt possimus enim?
